### ==========================================
### ⭐ REVIEW ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================
### Note: Reviews can only be submitted after a project is marked COMPLETED.
### Only the CLIENT can review the FREELANCER.

### Submit Review (Client only, project must be COMPLETED)
POST http://localhost:6868/api/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "projectId": "PROJECT_ID_HERE",
    "rating": 5,
    "comment": "Excellent work! Delivered ahead of schedule with great attention to detail. Highly recommended."
}

###

### Submit Review — 4 stars
POST http://localhost:6868/api/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "projectId": "PROJECT_ID_HERE",
    "rating": 4,
    "comment": "Good work overall. Communication could be improved but the final output was solid."
}

###

### Get All Reviews for a Freelancer
GET http://localhost:6868/api/review/freelancer/FREELANCER_ID_HERE

###
